                  "letterSpacing": 0.4
                },
                {
                  "id": "rft472",
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "The original stripe.charge() call had no idempotency key. If the network times out mid-request, a retry would create a duplicate charge.\n\nBy adding idempotencyKey: order.id, Stripe will deduplicate requests with the same key within 24 hours — preventing double-billing on retries.",
                  "x": 12,
                  "y": 34,
                  "width": 564,
                  "height": 48,
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width-height",
                  "fontSize": 11,
